sub_title: All in on life sciences - building the best lab infrastructure.
summary: Innovation and regulation in life science R&D are constantly fighting for the same resources. We founded Panorama Laboratories to create a lab environment where documentation is automatic and objective, so no time needs to be invested in documentation of R&D protocols/SOPs.
